<p>The Pretty Woman actress joined the likes of Jamie Lynn Spears, Awkwafina and Lea Michele, taking to the Instagram announcement to write 'Love you' with a series of kissing emojis.</p>

<p>Emma's Scream Queens co-star Lea - who recently gave birth to her own baby boy Ever Leo - also chimed in, writing: 'You will be the greatest mama! I love you Em! Boy moms together.'</p>

